category: Text
requires: cygwin glib2-runtime libaspell15 zlib
sdesc: "Interface to various spell checking libraries"
ldesc: "The project aims to provide an efficient extensible abstraction for
dealing with different spell checking libraries.

Enchant is meant to provide a generic interface into various existing
spell checking libaries. These include, but are not limited to:
    * Aspell/Pspell
    * Ispell
    * Hspell
    * Uspell
"
